# Tableau Dashboards

The interactive Tableau dashboards are published on Tableau Public and can be accessed using the links below.

🔗 **Financial Sales Overview**  
https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/fathy.raed/viz/Final_17842014441200/FinancialSalesOverview?publish=yes

🔗 **Product Inventory Performance**  
https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/fathy.raed/viz/Final_17842014441200/ProductInventoryPerformance?publish=yes

🔗 **Customer Geo-Insights**  
https://public.tableau.com/app/profile/fathy.raed/viz/Final_17842014441200/CustomerGeo-Insights?publish=yes

These dashboards provide:

- **Financial Sales Overview**
  - Revenue and profit analysis
  - Sales trends over time
  - Regional and category performance
  - Key financial KPIs

- **Product Inventory Performance**
  - Inventory status and stock levels
  - Product performance analysis
  - Category comparison
  - Inventory-related KPIs

- **Customer Geo-Insights**
  - Customer geographic distribution
  - Regional sales analysis
  - Location-based customer insights
  - Interactive maps and filters

> Click any of the links above to explore the interactive dashboards directly in Tableau Public.
